value.0: The Kaiburr crystal is a powerful glowing Force relic located on the planet Mimban. Local legend says that the god Pomojema uses the crystal to heal the wounded, but in reality it is the Force that is responsible. The crimson-colored gem has the ability to enhance Force powers.
